rComments: Nice guy. The seminar is more focused than the general US history course, which was quite broad and boring. Rewards attendance. Generous grader.

This professor was very good at taking the seminar in the right direction by basically knowing which questions to ask, and how to prompt students. As written before, he's very laid back and gives helpful comments on assignments.
teacherRatingTags: ['Participation matters', 'Gives good feedback', 'Get ready to read']

rComments: lol @ "Radio dj way of talking" - it's actually kinda true now that I think of it! Seems friendly and approachable, and classes were pretty laid-back. Helpful comments on assignments, and fair marker.
fun prof, pretty good class, has that whole "radio dj" way of speaking that's just amusing. Oh, and he's a REALLY generous marker (which doesn't hurt)
